LIST-START
ITEM: **Firewood**: any amount, always needed
ITEM: **Candles**: any amount, high priority
ITEM: **Honey**: any amount, we'll trade generously
ITEM: **Dried Meat**: any amount, always welcome
ITEM: **Mending Services**: clothing repair, blanket patching
ITEM: **Tool Sharpening**: axes, knives, shears
ITEM: **Soap**: handmade preferred
ITEM: **Eggs**: any amount, always useful
ITEM: **Seeds**: heirloom varieties preferred
ITEM: **Lumber**: any offcuts or split wood
LIST-END

