QUOTE: "Bring what you have, take what you need. We'll find a fair trade."

ALERT: success | New items added weekly! Stop by and see what's fresh.

TEXT: *All produce is grown without pesticides or synthetic fertilizers. We use rainwater collection and solar-powered cold storage. Please bring your own containers and bags. Every trade is negotiable: we believe in fair exchange, not fixed prices.*

